ization2star  aDer Band versammelt neue Beiträge zum Werk Adalbert Stifters und seiner Rezeption im 19. und 20. Jahrhundert. Einzelinterpretationen finden sich ebenso wie Untersuchungen größerer Motivkomplexe, Fragen der Textgenese werden ebenso behandelt wie solche der Wirkungsgeschichte. Am Schluß des Bandes steht die Erstveröffentlichung dreier Briefe Adalbert Stifters.  aThe volume assembles studies on the works of Adalbert Stifter (1805-1868) and the reception accorded to them in the 19th and 20th centuries. Alongside interpretations of individual works there are also studies of recurrent motifs, and the purview ranges from questions pertaining to the genesis of texts to issues posed by the history of their impact. The volume closes with the first-ever publication of three of Adalbert Stifter's letters.  aIssued also in print.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 29. Jun 2022) 7aLITERARY CRITICISM / European / German.2bisacsh1 aDittmann, Ulrich, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aDoppler, Alfred, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aFeilchenfeldt, Konrad, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aGottwald, Herwig, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aGreipl, Peter, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aHettche, Walter, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aHettche, Walter, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aHäntzschel, Günter, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aJohn, Johannes, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aJohn, Johannes, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aLachinger, Johann, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/r